Soon after its local arrival late last year, we were fortunate enough to get our hands on the Mercedes-AMG GT 63 S 4Matic+ 4-Door Coupe. Very impressed with the car’s superb handling to match it’s crazy pace, Road Test editor Mark Jones had this to say: ‘’The GT 63 S four-door coupe, in a nutshell, is a fast, dynamic car for the well-heeled family man who wants his high-powered GT fun, but needs the space and practicality of a full-sized family coupe.’’ But every well-heeled family man has his own little guilty pleasures in life and even in top end...